 良好英語 ;  懂讀寫中文 ;
 懂閱讀英文 ;   ; 具有較强的領導能力和組織協調能力，具有强烈的市場競爭意識和能力，有效地指導公司市場開拓和生産經營業務工作。 Job descriptions: T aking charge of the company's production, operation and management, taking full charge of the company's annual business objectives, and organizing the
 implementation of board resolutions;  Responsible for organizing the formulation and implementation of the company's annual business plan and investment plan;  Responsible for organizing the formulation of the company's internal management structure;  In accordance with the relevant procedures and decisions, appointing or dismissing managers other than those who should be appointed or dismissed by the board of directors;  Hosting the general manager's office meeting, deploying, supervising and coordinating the work of various departments:   Job Requirements Bachelor's degree; 10 years or above relevant working experience in power energy;  Cantonese speaking; Chinese speaking and reading; English speaking and reading;  Be familiar with the working mode and communication skills between the Mainland China and Hong Kong; Able to build rich relationships in different fields; Strong leadership, organization and coordination ability, strong sense of market competition and ability to effectively guide the company's market development, production and operation. Additional Information Career Level Top Qualification Degree Industry Job Function Years of Experience 10 years Employment Type Full Time Benefits Dental insurance, Double pay, Five-day work week, Flexible working hours, Medical insurance, Transportation allowance, Travel allowance Company details MicroGrid X International Energy Co., Ltd.(MGX) was established in Hong Kong SAR, China. It is an internet-powered energy company in the era of Internet of Things. It is engaged in the construction of microgrids, development of intelligent
 power distribution system, AI (artificial intelligence) technology research and development, application of big data analysis and blockchain technology in the energy sector. It is the world's first company applying big data analysis to the traditional energy
 dispatch system. It is a technology-based internet-powered energy company that integrates high-tech with traditional energy construction. There will also be technical support from the strategic partner of MGX. About JobsDB About jobsDB FAQ Career @ jobsDB Contact us Contact us International partners Bdjobs (Bandladesh) Brighter Monday (East Africa) Catho (Brazil) Jobberman (West Africa) JobStreet (S.E. Asia) Jora (Hong Kong) OCC Mundial (Mexico) Seaman Jobsite (Philippines) SEEK (Australia) Work Abroad (Philippines) Workana Zhaopin (China) Job Seekers Browse jobs Post resumes Job Alerts My jobsDB Career Insights Employers Post a job Search candidates Advertise with us Best Companies Connect Facebook Twitter jobsDB @ App Store jobsDB @ Google Play Privacy Statement Terms & Conditions Site Map Hong Kong (English) Privacy Statement Terms & Conditions Site Map Copyright © 1998-2019, jobsDB.
